description: With this skill you will be able to combine any ingredient in your kitchen. Just invoke Food Combinator and be prepared to eat the meal of your life.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask food combinator what pairs well with chicken
Alexa, ask food combinator about salmon
Alexa, ask food combinator what combines well with apricots
name: Food Combinator
shortDescription: Just provide an ingredient and Food Combinator will suggest the best products to mix it with
